1
00:00:00,167 --> 00:00:01,751
Name: Muhannad Mahmoud Saeed

2
00:00:01,834 --> 00:00:03,667
From the right side of the Old City

3
00:00:03,751 --> 00:00:05,876
Born on April 18, 1998

4
00:00:06,626 --> 00:00:08,918
I’m married, and I have two children

5
00:00:09,918 --> 00:00:13,417
I was detained on a Friday, on Eid al-Adha

6
00:00:14,375 --> 00:00:15,584
During the noon prayer

7
00:00:16,876 --> 00:00:17,876
I was standing guard

8
00:00:18,834 --> 00:00:21,125
My brother and I were working a machine to make fries and sell them

9
00:00:21,918 --> 00:00:24,000
At a place with children's rides

10
00:00:25,417 --> 00:00:29,125
Everyone left, and they told me to stay and guard the machine and the rides

11
00:00:30,042 --> 00:00:32,626
At that time, there was foot traffic

12
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:38,417
While I was selling, the Hisba Diwan car pulled up

13
00:00:38,417 --> 00:00:42,083
Even though one of those they call the Hisba

14
00:00:42,375 --> 00:00:44,042
Was the one who had made me stand guard

15
00:00:44,876 --> 00:00:46,500
They asked me to get in, but I told them I was standing guard

16
00:00:46,542 --> 00:00:48,918
He said, You are neglecting prayer
and selling at the time of prayer

17
00:00:49,626 --> 00:00:51,918
I refused to get into the car

18
00:00:52,667 --> 00:00:56,459
So he pushed me inside and shut the door on me

19
00:00:56,876 --> 00:01:01,417
Interviewer: According to you, you’d taken permission from one of them?

20
00:01:01,459 --> 00:01:03,918
Interviewer: Did he give you permission to stay and not go to prayer?
Witness: Yes

21
00:01:04,792 --> 00:01:07,834
Interviewer: Was the person you asked
permission from the same one who arrested you?

22
00:01:07,876 --> 00:01:09,209
Or was it another group who did that?

23
00:01:09,250 --> 00:01:10,709
No, another patrol came

24
00:01:11,125 --> 00:01:13,459
The one I asked permission from was standing in the square

25
00:01:13,918 --> 00:01:15,459
And I was standing by the triangle in the Sarj Khana area

26
00:01:15,459 --> 00:01:16,500
And he was blocking the road

27
00:01:16,584 --> 00:01:19,542
And the other came from the Grand Mosque and saw me

28
00:01:20,792 --> 00:01:23,334
I had taken permission and told him that
but he said, There is no such thing

29
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:24,792
I told him—We are two working on the machine

30
00:01:24,792 --> 00:01:28,042
One of us goes to pray and comes back, then the other goes to pray

31
00:01:30,083 --> 00:01:32,500
Interviewer: Couldn't the one who gave you permission see you?

32
00:01:32,834 --> 00:01:33,959
No, he was far from me

33
00:01:34,417 --> 00:01:35,459
Even if he could see me

34
00:01:35,709 --> 00:01:38,584
They wanted any pretext to hold someone to account

35
00:01:38,834 --> 00:01:39,959
To grab people

36
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:44,375
Interviewer: Then they made you get into the car. How did they treat you inside?

37
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:47,918
Did they swear at you or use obscene language?

38
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:50,876
Did they beat you? And did they blindfold you or not?
Witness: No, no

39
00:01:50,918 --> 00:01:52,918
Interviewer: From the moment you got into the car until you arrived here

40
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:55,083
They were two, and I became the third

41
00:01:55,125 --> 00:01:57,626
They only pushed me into the car at the start

42
00:01:57,876 --> 00:01:59,375
Because I refused to get into the car

43
00:01:59,918 --> 00:02:02,250
Because I had permission, so why take me and hold me to account?

44
00:02:02,792 --> 00:02:03,792
He did not accept that

45
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:06,083
In the car, no one spoke to me

46
00:02:06,918 --> 00:02:08,250
They brought us in, and we were three people

47
00:02:08,918 --> 00:02:12,918
Interviewer: Okay, the two who were with you in the car

48
00:02:13,459 --> 00:02:16,292
Do you remember exactly where they arrested them?

49
00:02:16,334 --> 00:02:17,334
And what were their charges?

50
00:02:17,375 --> 00:02:18,918
One of them was from Bawabat al-Sham

51
00:02:19,083 --> 00:02:20,083
He was at a wedding

52
00:02:21,042 --> 00:02:23,959
They caught him because he had plucked his eyebrows

53
00:02:24,542 --> 00:02:25,542
And he’d shaped his beard

54
00:02:25,876 --> 00:02:27,751
Interviewer: Do you mean he was the groom?

55
00:02:27,959 --> 00:02:30,751
No, he was one of the people in the wedding cars

56
00:02:30,792 --> 00:02:32,125
Interviewer: One of the guests?
Witness: Yes

57
00:02:32,205 --> 00:02:33,709
He was probably the groom’s paternal cousin

58
00:02:33,751 --> 00:02:36,167
Or his maternal cousin, I don’t remember exactly

59
00:02:36,792 --> 00:02:38,751
And the other was a young man

60
00:02:38,792 --> 00:02:40,667
His charge was neglecting prayer as well

61
00:02:42,083 --> 00:02:45,167
Interviewer: Were your eyes open?
Witness: Yes, open

62
00:02:46,083 --> 00:02:48,209
Interviewer: What was the exact time when they took you?

63
00:02:48,542 --> 00:02:51,250
I told you, at the noon prayer, exactly

64
00:02:51,918 --> 00:02:56,125
Meaning when the imam was giving the Friday sermon

65
00:02:56,459 --> 00:02:59,125
Interviewer: Okay, the place is narrow, a car can’t get in

66
00:02:59,125 --> 00:03:01,083
Where did the car come in from?

67
00:03:01,125 --> 00:03:03,167
And where did they drop you off, and how?

68
00:03:03,209 --> 00:03:04,500
And how did they bring you to this place?

69
00:03:04,751 --> 00:03:06,751
They stopped here where there is a yard

70
00:03:07,417 --> 00:03:09,000
They drove the car into it

71
00:03:09,459 --> 00:03:11,125
They brought us here on foot

72
00:03:12,167 --> 00:03:14,626
Interviewer: On foot, in front of everyone, just normally?

73
00:03:14,792 --> 00:03:16,209
Yes, it was normal in front of people

74
00:03:16,918 --> 00:03:18,000
Interviewer: And they brought you here?

75
00:03:18,083 --> 00:03:19,209
They brought us inside here

76
00:03:20,834 --> 00:03:23,876
There were prisoners inside

77
00:03:24,209 --> 00:03:25,751
Interviewer: Didn’t you stay here for a long time?

78
00:03:25,792 --> 00:03:27,834
And was the door open when you entered or closed?

79
00:03:27,918 --> 00:03:29,626
It was open, as it is now

80
00:03:30,542 --> 00:03:31,918
But as soon as we entered, they closed it
